<br>
We don't know, we will not know until Verant releases more information. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujochangaladar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jochan Galadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 622<br> <font color=#333333>(9/26/02 1:19:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=38.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will new PoP pets make epic pet obsolete?</span><hr size=1> There's a lot of magician pride concerning their epics, as even though Epics are Kunark era, the mag epic was basically a broken quest until Velious.  That being said, magicians are likely the last class to want their epic to be replaced by something better that may likely be a simple drop.<br>
<br>
