Dmuerte <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uravenspirermerquise.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravenspire R Merquise</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(9/26/02 7:12:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=38.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: will new pop pets make epic pet obsolete?</span><hr size=1> <br>
