<br>
1)  Comparing any epic to any other epic is completely relevant.  People use epics for the effect they have. ( And no, I do not mean strictly thigns like &quot;effect: random effect&quot;.)  Rogues use theirs to do damage.  Warriors use theirs to hold agro.  Mages use theirs to................... make a pet.  The stats could disappear and all these items would still be in use..though casters would bag theirs immediately..  It looks like necros epics will be obsolete for real use this expansion..if it wasn't already...ours can be aswell without too much hassle.<br>
